room_title: Escape room "The Rise of Dracula" by Escape Room Novi in Detroit
room_address: 44325 W 12 Mile Ste H175 Novi, MI 48377
room_description: Welcome to the home of Vladimir Tepes. Better known as Count Dracula. The count has been deceased for over 500 years. His Mistress is doing everything in her power to bring Vlad back to life. She has figured out if she can put enough of her blood along with human blood he can be brought back to life. She has already started the contraption. Your goal is to find this contraption, shut it down, open up Vladimir’s coffin and stake him one last time…It won’t be easy. They know your coming. Good luck.
